5 provided in subsection E of this section, “inducement” means
6 directly or indirectly offering, selling, trading, giving or
7 furnishing any discount, free goods, electronic or nonelectronic
8 refrigerated equipment, barrels, tubs, fixtures, dispensing
9 equipment, outdoor electric or nonelectric advertising structure
10 displaying the retailer’s name, permanent shelving, supplies, gifts,
