19 conducting janitorial services, providing decorations, samples of
20 alcoholic beverages, personal property or other inducement or thing
21 of value to any retail spirit, retail beer, retail wine, beer and
22 wine, mixed beverage, caterer, bottle club or special event
23 licensee, wine and spirits wholesaler or beer distributor, their
24 agents or employees.
